</taxonomicName>
in known only from southeastern 
<collectingRegion box="[188,284,272,298]" country="United States of America" name="Arizona" pageId="21" pageNumber="246">Arizona</collectingRegion>
. Collecting dates range from early June to mid-July and early to late September.
</paragraph>
